Template: custom-conf-pam-krb5_opensc/crl-type
Type: select
Choices: none, online, offline, auto
Default: none
Description: Certificates Revocation List (CRL) type ?
 Please select the type of Certificates Revocation List (CRL) to check the
 presented certificate's revocation status:
 .
  - none:    no revocation check is performed
  - online:  the CRL is downloaded from the certificate's CRL distribution point
  - offline: the local CRL is used (/etc/ssl/local/localsite-auth-crl.pem)
  - auto:    try 'online' and fail back to 'offline'

